  "texts": [
    "This raises the following research questions (RQ) for the task of sequential sentence classification: #RQ1To what extent are datasets from different domains semantically related?",
    "#RQ2 Which transfer learning approach works best?",
    "#RQ3 Which neural network layers are transferable under which constraints?",
    "#RQ4 Is it beneficial to train a multi-task model with multiple datasets?",
    "Typically, every dataset has a domain-specific annotation scheme that consists of a set of associated sentence classes."
